	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm trying to do the level select cheat.  I Googled it and got this over and over:  "Select adventure mode. Press Start, A, Select, B on controller two during game play. Then, press Right for the Mall, Left for the Beach, or Up for the Planet level."  That doesn't really help me too much.  
<br />
<br />The closest I seem to come is pressing Start to get the character intros, then a second time to get the storyline, then a third time to get the "Level 1" screen (this is all in fairly quick succession), then rapidly pressing Start, A, Select, B on controller 2 and Up on controller 1.  All that does is begin level 1 upon pressing Up on controller 1, no matter how fast or slow I enter the code. 
<br />
<br />Has anyone ever gotten this cheat to work?  How -exactly- is it done?  I tried this cheat when I was 13 and never got it to work then, and now 13 years later, I still can't get it to work.  Someone please help before I kill someone at Electronic Arts.

		

